License: ISC
Comment:
 The tarball is repacked because upstream uses the waf build system, which is
 shipped in the tarball as a binary blob. The binary includes the source,
 but Debian considers that backwards, so we run a debian/repack-waf script to
 fix that. See also: https://wiki.debian.org/UnpackWaf

